text: Piampatara humeralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1916 and is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Piampatara humeralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1916
title: Piampatara humeralis
